data.description:
A spacious home and functional split level design. Living room, eat-in kitchen and spacious family room addition on main level. Three bedrooms and full bathroom on upper level. Large, L-shaped rec room with closet space, mechanical area, laundry room and 2nd bathroom in the lower level. Nice 22 x 14' cement patio in rear with awning cover. Two car, detached garage with newer automatic opener - new key pad and roller pins replaced. Situated on an approximate, 50 x 169' lot with fenced-in rear yard; rear boundary line is approximately 60' wide.

The kitchen is huge with ample cabinetry and counter tops! Family room in rear with vaulted ceiling, skylight and corner fireplace with gas logs. Hardwood flooring, vinyl replacement windows and some recent updates in upper level bathroom. Newer storm doors at front and side entries. Kitchen appliances along with the washer & dryer included. Seller is proactively offering a home warranty. 

The home needs extensive updating yet habitable and priced accordingly ... great potential!
